

   Front-End Tech/Tools
   ------------------------
   

   Language 
   
     --> Javascript  
     
   Module spec
   
     --> commonJS  
     --> ES6 modules ( future )
    
   Transpilers/compilers/polyfils
   
     --> babel ( best )
     --> typescript compiler  ( if code code written in Typescript) 

    Mudule Bundler / Loader ( build )  
   
     --> Webpack 
     
    Testing F.Ws
    
     --> Mocha  + assertion and mock libraries
     
    Test Runners
    
     --> karma ( unit )
     --> Protractor  ( e2e )
     
     
     JS Libraries and F.Ws
     
     --> React  : View Library
         or
     --> Angular-2 : Framework  ( new )
     
        +
        
        other functional-libraries
     
     
     State Management Libraries
     
     --> Flux Pattern
     
         impln : Redux
         
      
      Responsive View F.Ws
      
      --> bootstrap
      
      or
      
      --> Material UI F.ws  ( future )
      
                  
         
